w-americans-are-thinking-about-aging/</link><description>从他们认为自己衰老的程度到如何评价自己的身心健康和财务安全，高收入的老年人比中收入或低收入的老年人表现得更好。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Nov 2025 00:50:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/social-trends/2025/11/06/how-americans-are-thinking-about-aging/</guid></item><item><title>ADP 就业数据与劳工统计局官方就业报告的比较</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2025/11/05/how-adp-employment-data-compares-with-official-bls-jobs-reports/</link><description>当无法获得美国劳工统计局的报告时，许多经济观察人士会转向 ADP 的全国就业报告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Nov 2025 01:06:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2025/11/05/how-adp-employment-data-compares-with-official-bls-jobs-reports/</guid></item></channel></rss>